claim.claim-text:
A method for managing data in an electronic device, the method comprising:
Detecting (1403) a request for tagging a data record;
selecting (1405) a portion of the data record in response to the request;
identifying a content item based on the selected portion of the data record; and
associating the content item with the data record.

An electronic device (1701) comprising:
an input unit (1750) for receiving a request for tagging a data record; and
a processor configured to:
detect the request for tagging the data record;
select a portion of the data record in response to the request;
identify a content item based on the selected portion of the data record;
and
associate the content item with the data record.
